	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />E la carta è<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Come promesso, eccoti <tag a="50" b="1" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />. È tu<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x12 0xcd00 0x2 0x6f 0x2 0x61 0x0" />! <delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Mantengo sempre la parola data.<pageBreak />Sempre ammesso che tu non voglia
